data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
Make sure you have your PA8 files in a folder named "mons" next to this exe before running this mode. This mode is CPU intensive and may freeze your computer while it calculates. We are not liable for any damages occured when using this mode, use at your own risk.
Once it calculates your seed head to the non-cfw pathfinder tab to find the path to your preferred pokemon.
This mode is just a GUI interface for Kurt's work and pretty much all credit goes to him.
